This is how to build Zombie Dash, assuming you've
already installed freeGLUT:

1.Install freeglut

Ubuntu: sudo apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev
Fedora: sudo yum install freeglut freeglut-devel

2. To build the program, change your directory into the ZombieDash directory and type
	make

3. To run the program, type
	./ZombieDash
